heading: Conclave Dungeon Guide
content: Conclave is slow dungeon with the highly annoying Search the Slain objective and the , making it a poor choice for Nightmare Dungeons and first clears. The Cultists can be challenging on higher difficulties, so don't use this one for pushing Nightmare Dungeons either. But if you just need to slam an easy Sigil with no other options, give it a shot. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
